Barlow Outfitting is proud to be an Equal Opportunity Service Provider.

WYOMING HIGH COUNTRY TROPHY HUNTS
WELCOME TO WONDERFUL WYOMING!
Barlow Outfitting offers Wyoming Elk, Moose, Bighorn Sheep, Mountain Goat, Mule Deer, Whitetail Deer, Antelope, Combination, Black Bear, and Mountain Lion hunts, drop camps and horseback trail rides. We take pride in the level of unsurpassed service to our clients and the best High Country Trophy Hunts.

 
We hunt several Big Game units in Western and north central Wyoming. Mobility is the key to Trophy Big Game hunting.

To request a brochure, references and/or a price list, give us a call at (307) 413-0726 or contact us by e-mail at barlowoutfitting@gmail.com. We look forward to the opportunity of sharing our great passion and enthusiasm of the Wyoming wilderness with you.
